{
  "uid": "lgtm-route-drilldown",
  "title": "02 - Route Drilldown (Logs/Traces)",
  "tags": ["lgtm", "observability", "drilldown"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "route",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "route (http.route)",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": "",
        "sort": 1,
        "definition": "label_values(http_server_requests_seconds_count, uri)",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(http_server_requests_seconds_count, uri)",
          "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
        },
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "Explore Tempo (route)",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/explore?orgId=1&left=%7B%22datasource%22%3A%22tempo%22%2C%22queries%22%3A%5B%7B%22refId%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22query%22%3A%22http.route%3D%5C%22${route:percentencode}%5C%22%22%2C%22queryType%22%3A%22traceql%22%7D%5D%2C%22range%22%3A%7B%22from%22%3A%22now-15m%22%2C%22to%22%3A%22now%22%7D%7D",
      "targetBlank": true
    },
    {
      "title": "Explore Loki (route)",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/explore?orgId=1&left=%7B%22datasource%22%3A%22loki%22%2C%22queries%22%3A%5B%7B%22refId%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22expr%22%3A%22%7Bcompose_service%3D~%5C%22gateway%7Corder-service%7Cpayment-service%5C%22%7D%20%7C%3D%20%5C%22${route:percentencode}%5C%22%22%2C%22queryType%22%3A%22range%22%7D%5D%2C%22range%22%3A%7B%22from%22%3A%22now-15m%22%2C%22to%22%3A%22now%22%7D%7D",
      "targetBlank": true
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to use",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "1) 위에서 `route`(http.route)를 선택합니다.\\n\\n2) 아래 Logs 패널에서 에러/타임아웃 로그를 확인합니다.\\n\\n3) Trace까지 보고 싶으면 상단의 **Explore Tempo (route)** 링크로 이동합니다.\\n\\nTip: 이 데모는 `{compose_service=~\\\"gateway|order-service|payment-service\\\"}` 로그만 보여줍니다."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "App logs (errors)",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "{compose_service=~\"gateway|order-service|payment-service\"} |= \"${route}\" |= \"ERROR\""
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "dedupStrategy": "none"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Top 10 routes by 5xx (rate)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "links": [
            {
              "title": "Filter this route",
              "url": "/d/lgtm-route-drilldown/02-route-drilldown?var-route=${__field.labels.uri}&from=${__from}&to=${__to}",
              "targetBlank": false
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) by (uri))"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Top 10 routes by p95 (seconds)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "links": [
            {
              "title": "Filter this route",
              "url": "/d/lgtm-route-drilldown/02-route-drilldown?var-route=${__field.labels.uri}&from=${__from}&to=${__to}",
              "targetBlank": false
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le, uri)))"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
